title: the anniversary man
description:
The anniversary man by R.J. Ellory


John Costello and his girlfriend suffered an attack from the psychopathic "Hammer of God" murderer in New Jersey. 

He survived at the price of psychological incapacity, working as a crime researcher for a newspaper. 

A detective is working on the death of a 15-year-old girl along with a reporter whose source is the damaged John Costello. 

They join forces to track down a psychopath.


the reviews the book got are rather harsh, but i think it's gripping. At least it's a good beach read.
